  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether ICD(Implantable Cardioverter Defibrillator)
      implantation on the top of optimal medical therapy in patients with variant angina
      manifesting as aborted sudden cardiac death reduces the incidence of the death from any cause
      compared with optimal medical therapy alone.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
